(firstQuint)Preparing for Kidney Transplant by Attaining a Healthy Weight.

 The goal of this study is to prepare subjects for kidney transplant.

 Patients who are in need of a kidney transplant but are unable to be place on the wait list due to weight will be enrolled in a six month workout program.

 The workout program will consist of counseling from a registered dietician, personal training from certified trainers and constant health monitoring.

